  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Part-Time Digital Marketing Manager",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for a <strong>young, dynamic and creative Digital Marketing Manager</strong> to support two of our yoga studio brands. This is a part-time role ideal for someone who loves <strong>content creation, social media, and wellness</strong> — yoga/fitness background is a bonus!</p><h3><strong>💼 Job Scope & Responsibilities</strong></h3><p><strong>Content Creation & Studio Visits</strong></p><ul><li><p>Visit the studio <strong>twice a week</strong> (1 hour each time) for <strong>video and photo shooting</strong></p></li><li><p>Video editing & creation of short-form content (Reels, TikTok, YouTube Shorts)</p></li></ul><p><strong>Social Media Management</strong></p><ul><li><p>Manage <strong>two social media accounts</strong></p></li><li><p>Create and schedule <strong>3 posts per week per account</strong></p></li><li><p>Plan and execute <strong>paid ads</strong> (FB/IG/Google) to drive lead generation</p></li><li><p>Grow audience reach, engagement, and conversions</p></li><li><p>Respond to WhatsApp/IG enquiries and forward them to the studio</p></li></ul><p><strong>Design & Marketing Collateral</strong></p><ul><li><p>Create <strong>event posters</strong> (minimum 3 per month)</p></li><li><p>Simple graphic design for promotions & studio announcements</p></li></ul><p><strong>Website & Content</strong></p><ul><li><p>Update and manage website information</p></li><li><p>Write clear, attractive content for classes, workshops, and events</p></li><li><p>Manage SEO basics (titles, tags, descriptions)</p></li></ul><p><strong>Analytics & Reporting</strong></p><ul><li><p>Weekly and monthly reporting on:</p><ul><li><p>Lead generation</p></li><li><p>Engagement</p></li><li><p>Ad performance</p></li><li><p>Growth metrics</p></li></ul></li></ul><h3><strong>🧠 Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Minimum <strong>3 years of experience</strong> in digital marketing or social media</p></li><li><p>Skilled in:</p><ul><li><p>Social media ads (FB/IG/Google)</p></li><li><p>Video shooting & editing</p></li><li><p>Graphic design (Canva/Adobe)</p></li><li><p>Content writing</p></li></ul></li><li><p>Must be able to work independently and deliver results</p></li><li><p>Has interest or experience in <strong>yoga and fitness</strong> (bonus)</p></li></ul><h3><strong>⏰ Working Arrangement</strong></h3><ul><li><p><strong>Studio visit:</strong> 2 times per week, 1 hour each</p></li><li><p><strong>Rest of work:</strong> Work from home</p></li><li><p>Flexible schedule for editing, posting & ad management</p></li><li><p>Immediate start</p></li></ul><h3><strong>💰 Monthly Budget</strong></h3><p><strong>$1,500</strong> per month</p>",
